source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04401_000010_YUGIRI<tab>Make ready, friends. We are come to the Burn.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04401_000010_YUGIRI<tab>Nous y sommes<var 1D /var>! Les terres désolées de L'Escarre<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04401_000020_HIEN<tab>Everyone! Land where you can! We must wait out the storm!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04401_000020_HIEN<tab>Quel vent...<var 1D /var>! Vous m'entendez<var 1D /var>!? Descendez tous<var 1D /var>! On continue à pied<var 1D /var>!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_04401_000050_SUZAKU<tab>Mon aramitama... Je le sens qui se réveille... Aaah... Aaaaaaaah<var 1D /var>!
